data.description: THIS HOME QUALIFIES FOR FHA ASSUMABLE INTEREST RATE 5.25%. GORGEOUS GRAND HOME. THIS BEAUTIFUL 4 BEDROOM HOME WITH 3 FULL BATHS IN THE MASTER PLANNED GRAND PENINSULA COMMUNITY FEATURING A LARGE CLUB HOUSE, TWO SWIMMING POOLS, TWO PLAYGROUNDS, HIKING, BIKING, JOGGING TRAILS, PARKS, AND COMMUNITY PONDS WITH EASY ACCESS TO FREEWAY, LAKE, SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, AND RESTAURANTS. AS YOU WALK IN, YOU ARE GREETED BY RICH WOOD FLOORS AND THE BEAUTIFUL ARCHES AND GRAND ENTRANCE FOYER WITH FORMAIL DINING ROOM.  THE HOME HAS AN OPEN FLOORPLAN WITH HIGH CEILINGS. THE LARGE LIVING ROOM OPENS TO THE KITCHEN AND BREAKFAST NOOK. THE KITCHEN IS A CHEF'S DREAM WITH PLENTY OF CABINET SPACE, STORAGE, SHELVES, AND ISLAND. LARGE MASTER BEDROOM DOWNSTAIRS WITH MASTER BATH, AND DREAM CLOSET. SPLIT GUEST BEDROOMS ON THE OPPOSITE SIDE OF THE HOUSE ON THE FIRST FLOOR, PLUS A GAMEROOM UPSTAIRS AND MEDIA ROOM OR 4TH BEDROOM. BIG BACK YARD WITH BEAUTIFUL PERGOLA WITH AN OUTDOOR KITCHEN AND FIREPLACE.
